org.gridgain.grid.cache.query
Interface GridCacheQueryFuture<T>

All Superinterfaces:
Callable<Collection<T>>, GridFuture<Collection<T>>, GridIterable<T>, GridIterator<T>, GridMetadataAware, GridSerializableIterator<T>, Iterable<T>, Iterator<T>, Serializable
public interface GridCacheQueryFuture<T>
extends GridFuture<Collection<T>>, GridIterable<T>

Cache query future returned by GridCacheQuery.execute(GridProjection...) or by analogous methods on GridCacheReduceQuery and GridCacheTransformQuery. Refer to corresponding query javadoc documentation for more information.
